nes (defensive tackle, born 1994)}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Curtis|last=Virges|num=98|pos=DL|class=Sr|link=}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=John|last=Harris|num=99|pos=DL|class=Jr|link=}}\n|special_teams_players=\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Westin|last=Graves|num=35|pos=K|class=Fr|link=}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Winston|last=Chapman|num=38|pos=LS|class=Jr|link=}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Devon|last=Bell|num=40|pos=K/P|class=Jr|link=}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Evan|last=Sobiesk|num=41|pos=K|class=So|link=}}\n{{American football roster/Player|first=Logan|last=Cooke|num=43|pos=K/P|class=Fr|link=}}\n}}\n{{American football roster/Footer|roster_url=http://www.hailstate.com/SportSelect.dbml?SPSID=90891&SPID=10997&DB_OEM_ID=16800&Q_SEASON=2014|accessdate=May 3, 2015\n\n|head_coach=\n*[[Dan Mullen]] \u2013 6th year\n|asst_coach=\n* Billy Gonzales ([[Offensive coordinator|Co-OC]]/Wide Receivers) \u2013 2nd year\n*John Hevesy ([[Offensive coordinator|Co-OC]]/Offensive Linemen) \u2013 6th year\n*[[Brian Johnson (quarterback)|Brian Johnson]] (Quarterbacks) \u2013 1st year\n*[[Greg Knox]] (Running backs) \u2013 6th year\n*Scott Sallach (Tight ends) \u2013 6th year\n*[[Geoff Collins (American football)|Geoff Collins]] ([[Defensive coordinator|DC]]/Linebackers) \u2013 4th year\n*Tony Hughes (Safeties) \u2013 5th year\n*[[Deshea Townsend]] (Cornerbacks) \u2013 2nd year\n*David Turner (Defensive Linemen) \u2013 2nd year\n}}\n\n==Schedule==\n{{CFB schedule\n| rankyear = 2014\n| poll = [[2014 NCAA Division I FBS football rankings#AP Poll|AP Poll]] released prior to game\n| timezone = Central\n\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = August 30\n| time = 6:30 p.m.\n| w/l = w\n| nonconf = y\n| rank = \n| opponent = [[2014 Southern Miss Golden Eagles football team|Southern Miss]]\n| site_stadium = [[Davis Wade Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Starkville, Mississippi|Starkville, MS]]\n| tv = [[SEC Network|SECN]]