roop ships of the War Shipping Administration]]\n[[Category:Hospital ships of the United States Army]]\n", "name_user": "Telecineguy", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eBattle of Dutch Harbor:<ref>[http://www.usmm.org/heroes.html usmm.org Heroes] </ref>", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USAHS_Marigold"}
